    "content": [
        {
            "type": "text/html",
            "language": null,
            "base": "https://webview.tech/category/podcast/feed/",
            "value": "<div class=\"markdown-here-wrapper\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1.2em !important;\">我们为什么爱看评论？怎样的人类文字最有效率？更「好」的手机设计、APP 设计？APP Store 已经十年了？</p>\n<h2 id=\"show-note-\" style=\"margin: 1.3em 0px 1em; padding: 0px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 1.4em; border-bottom: 1px solid #eeeeee;\">SHOW NOTE：</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul-list\">\n<li class=\"md-list-item\">\n<p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" contenteditable=\"true\"><span class=\"md-plain\">喜讯：敬礼的小程序比赛获奖了</span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<ul class=\"ul-list\">\n<li class=\"md-list-item\">\n<p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" contenteditable=\"true\"><span class=\"md-plain\">回归微博：</span><span class=\"md-link\"><a href=\"http://weibo.com/recwangyin\"><span class=\"md-plain\">@王隐在录音</span></a></span></p>\n<ul class=\"ul-list\">\n<li class=\"md-list-item\">\n<p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" contenteditable=\"true\"><span class=\"md-plain\">推特</span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<ul class=\"ul-list\">\n<li class=\"md-list-item\">\n<p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" contenteditable=\"true\"><span class=\"md-plain\">对微博的错误偏见、正确定位</span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<ul class=\"ul-list\">\n<li class=\"md-list-item\">\n<p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" contenteditable=\"true\"><span class=\"md-plain\">「粉丝」、「Follower」</span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<ul class=\"ul-list\">\n<li class=\"md-list-item\">\n<p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" contenteditable=\"true\"><span class=\"md-plain\">时间线：关注的人，第三方客户端</span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<ul class=\"ul-list\">\n<li class=\"md-list-item\">\n<p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" contenteditable=\"true\"><span class=\"md-plain\">为什么我们爱（看）评论和点赞（知乎、新闻、音乐 APP）</span></p>\n<ul class=\"ul-list\">\n<li class=\"md-list-item\">\n<p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" contenteditable=\"true\"><span class=\"md-plain\">对比 Quora 、知乎</span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<ul class=\"ul-list\">\n<li class=\"md-list-item\">\n<p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" contenteditable=\"true\"><span class=\"md-plain\">不鼓励点赞、评论的社区</span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<ul class=\"ul-list\">\n<li class=\"md-list-item\">\n<p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" contenteditable=\"true\"><span class=\"md-link\"><a href=\"https://www.quora.com/Why-do-so-many-view-and-not-comment-on-Quora\"><span class=\"md-plain\">为什么不应该鼓励评论（quora）</span></a></span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<ul class=\"ul-list\">\n<li class=\"md-list-item\">\n<p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" contenteditable=\"true\"><span class=\"md-plain\">情绪、理性</span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<ul class=\"ul-list\">\n<li class=\"md-list-item\">\n<p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" contenteditable=\"true\"><span class=\"md-plain\">文字效率的优越性，概括性评论，人懒了</span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<ul class=\"ul-list\">\n<li class=\"md-list-item\">\n<p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" contenteditable=\"true\"><span class=\"md-plain\">社区的必然衰亡性</span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<ul class=\"ul-list\">\n<li class=\"md-list-item\">\n<p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" contenteditable=\"true\"><span class=\"md-plain\">答案属于社区，问题能属于个人吗？</span></p>\n<ul class=\"ul-list\">\n<li class=\"md-list-item\">\n<p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" contenteditable=\"true\"><span class=\"md-plain\">问题删除权，编辑权</span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<ul class=\"ul-list\">\n<li class=\"md-list-item\">\n<p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" contenteditable=\"true\"><span class=\"md-plain\">人类的语言体系和文字体系是否应该一致</span></p>\n<ul class=\"ul-list\">\n<li class=\"md-list-item\">\n<p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" contenteditable=\"true\"><span class=\"md-plain\">为什么计算机语言上层可以不统一（C，java，go）</span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<ul class=\"ul-list\">\n<li class=\"md-list-item\">\n<p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" contenteditable=\"true\"><span class=\"md-plain\">《</span><span class=\" md-link\"><a href=\"https://book.douban.com/subject/26295448/\"><span class=\"md-plain\">你一生的故事</span></a></span><span class=\"md-plain\">》七肢桶</span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<ul class=\"ul-list\">\n<li class=\"md-list-item\">\n<p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" contenteditable=\"true\"><span class=\"md-plain\">人类语言使用中文，文字使用阿拉伯数字是否可以提高沟通效率</span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<ul class=\"ul-list\">\n<li class=\"md-list-item\">\n<p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" contenteditable=\"true\"><span class=\"md-plain\">模块化；人类规避基因缺陷</span></p>\n<ul class=\"ul-list\">\n<li class=\"md-list-item\">\n<p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" contenteditable=\"true\"><span class=\"md-link\"><a href=\"https://www.guokr.com/article/441076/\"><span class=\"md-plain\">思维殿堂</span></a></span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<ul class=\"ul-list\">\n<li class=\"md-list-item\">\n<p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" contenteditable=\"true\"><span class=\"md-plain\">更「好」的 APP 设计</span></p>\n<ul class=\"ul-list\">\n<li class=\"md-list-item\">\n<p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" contenteditable=\"true\"><span class=\"md-plain\">搜索框的位置：</span><span class=\" md-link\"><a href=\"https://uxdesign.cc/what-every-product-designer-should-take-away-from-lyfts-new-ui-742c9668b067\"><span class=\"md-plain\">What every product designer should take away from Lyft’s new UI</span></a></span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<ul class=\"ul-list\">\n<li class=\"md-list-item\">\n<p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" contenteditable=\"true\"><span class=\"md-plain\">用户习惯：房屋中的坑</span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<ul class=\"ul-list\">\n<li class=\"md-list-item\">\n<p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" contenteditable=\"true\"><span class=\"md-plain\">更「好」的手机设计</span></p>\n<ul class=\"ul-list\">\n<li class=\"md-list-item\">\n<p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" contenteditable=\"true\"><span class=\"md-plain\">优化 Universal Links</span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<ul class=\"ul-list\">\n<li class=\"md-list-item\">\n<p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" contenteditable=\"true\"><span class=\"md-plain\">APP 全局 ajax</span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<ul class=\"ul-list\">\n<li class=\"md-list-item\">\n<p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" contenteditable=\"true\"><span class=\"md-plain\">排版设计（字体）是否是「内容」一部分</span></p>\n<ul class=\"ul-list\">\n<li class=\"md-list-item\">\n<p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" contenteditable=\"true\"><span class=\"md-plain\">中文字体趋同</span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<ul class=\"ul-list\">\n<li class=\"md-list-item\">\n<p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" contenteditable=\"true\"><span class=\"md-plain\">排版是「附加」功能？</span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<ul class=\"ul-list\">\n<li class=\"md-list-item\">\n<p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" contenteditable=\"true\"><span class=\"md-plain\">APP Store 10 年</span></p>\n<ul class=\"ul-list\">\n<li class=\"md-list-item\">\n<p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" contenteditable=\"true\"><span class=\"md-plain\">第一个 APP</span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<ul class=\"ul-list\">\n<li class=\"md-list-item\">\n<p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" contenteditable=\"true\"><span class=\"md-plain\">PC 到移动互联网的惊讶</span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"md-list-item md-focus-container\">\n<p class=\"md-end-block md-p md-focus\" contenteditable=\"true\"><span class=\"md-plain md-expand\">更正：upvote 说成 update 了</span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"playlist-\" style=\"margin: 1.3em 0px 1em; padding: 0px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 1.4em; border-bottom: 1px solid #eeeeee;\">Playlist：</h2>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1.2em !important;\">狗尿馆 &#8211; 万能青年旅店</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1.2em !important;\">不醉不归 &#8211; 徐佳莹</p>\n<h2 id=\"-\" style=\"margin: 1.3em 0px 1em; padding: 0px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 1.4em; border-bottom: 1px solid #eeeeee;\">主持/嘉宾：</h2>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1.2em !important;\">王隐（<a href=\"http://weibo.com/recwangyin\">@王隐在录音</a>）</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1.2em !important;\">敬礼</p>\n<h2 id=\"-\" style=\"margin: 1.3em 0px 1em; padding: 0px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 1.4em; border-bottom: 1px solid #eeeeee;\">联系我们：</h2>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1.2em !important;\">你可以通过邮件向我们反馈节目中的问题和建议： <a href=\"mailto://hi@webview.tech\">hi@webview.tech</a></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1.2em !important;\">微博：<a href=\"http://weibo.com/recwangyin\">@王隐在录音</a></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1.2em !important;\">我们的网站： <a href=\"